```r

  filter(year == "2000") %>%
  group_by(country) %>% 
  summarize(overall = sum(catch, na.rm = TRUE)) %>% 
  arrange(desc(overall)) %>% 
  top_n(5)
```

```r

  filter(ASFIS_sciname == "Sardina pilchardus") %>%

  group_by(country) %>%
```
